    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I've babied it since day one, and it shows. If you\u2019re looking for a total stunner that\u2019s been meticulously cared for, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
