    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. It is seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I have taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. If you are looking for something that feels brand new without that brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
