    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood, the S54B32 inline-six features a fully serviced high-pressure VANOS system and synchronized individual throttle bodies, ensuring razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power band to the 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise shifts, sending power through a refreshed M-Variable limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates and epoxy injection to exceed factory structural tolerances. The chassis retains its original suspension geometry, augmented only by high-performance dampers that preserve the car's legendary N\u00fcrburgring-tuned kinematics. Finished in impeccable Carbon Black Metallic, the exterior shows no signs of road rash or oxidation, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with zero bolster wear. This is a concours-level specimen for the driver who demands mechanical perfection.",
